Package: paramlink2
Type: Package
Title: Parametric Linkage Analysis
Version: 0.9.9000
Authors@R: person("Magnus Dehli", "Vigeland", 
                  email = "m.d.vigeland@medisin.uio.no", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9134-4962"))
Description: Parametric linkage analysis of monogenic traits in medical 
    pedigrees. Features include singlepoint analysis, multipoint analysis 
    (through a wrapper to the 'MERLIN' software), visualisation of LOD 
    scores and summaries of linkage peaks.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/magnusdv/paramlink2
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-GB
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5),
    pedtools
Imports: 
    pedprobr,
    forrel
Suggests: 
    testthat
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
